item.description: About I’m Wei-Hsiang (Matt) Wang, from Taiwan. I’m a software engineer at Umbo Computer Vision focusing primarily on the development of realtime human detection pipeline in Python & Node.js. I received both of my B.S. (2016) & M.S. (2018) in Mechanical Engineering from National Taiwan University (NTU). Also a cat slave to a tabby named Mujo & a calico named Muya.
